The worst trait of a "talking head" on any investment site, on the business news media platforms or contained in their services --- is selective recall. Its a disease inflicted by far too many who seem to think they can deceive the individual investor.

The hubris in the media is always something to behold. But, recently it has gotten ever more self confident. To me, the only certainty is the lack of certainty with so many political, geopolitical, economic and market outcomes possible. With many of those outcomes adverse.
To many are merchants of attention who are trying to sell individual investors a service by hooking them on to nonsense and jibberish.
